OBSERVATIONS FROM THE ABOVE UNIVARIATE ANALYSIS

SMOKER: shows the number of no smokers(1064) is more than the number of smokers(274) in Plateau. AGE: Shows the report covers age from 18-64yrs with majority of the age population between 18 and 36yrs amounting to about 60% of the insurance coverage. CHARGES: The visualization shows that majotiry of the charges incured falls within 1000 to 5000 with the least charge at 1121.

The above visualization shows that smoking habit depends on region considering the non smokers of each region is relative to the smokers. Southeast has the highest number of smokers(91) and non smokers(273). Whilst Northeast has the lowest non smokers(257) and smokers(67). In all, the number of non smokers is higher than the numbers of smokers signifying a healthy community/State.
